nib.text:
A woman was fatally stabbed in North End Sunday afternoon.

Shortly before 2:30 p.m., police responded to a report of a stabbing in the 100 block of Larpenteur Avenue West.

Upon arrival, officers discovered a woman with a stab wound to the chest.

Medics pronounced her deceased at the scene, a spokesperson from the SPPD said.

No arrests have been made. Homicide detectives ask anyone with information to call them at (651) 266-5650.
